{"tid":2334410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲有確診患者帶有變種武肺病毒 兩名患者是來自英國的遊客","createTime":"2020-12-21T07:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T07:38:24.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59b43ac6e67d73e1c493142921ea6b92a5ce7945","tid":2334410,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:09:23.000Z","msg":"澳洲有確診患者帶有變種新型冠狀病毒<br />\n<br />\n繼荷蘭、意大利等地後，澳洲亦有確診患者帶有英國發現的變種新型冠狀病毒。當局指，兩名患者是來自英國的遊客，在酒店檢疫期間確診。<br />\n<br />\n英國發現傳染率高七成的變種新型冠狀病毒，形容新毒株是「致命病毒」，已經失去控制，首相約翰遜周一主持緊急會議，商討國際旅行措施，同進出英國的貨運。多國嚴防病毒傳入，荷蘭、比利時、奧地利、意大利等禁止來自英國的航班。沙特阿拉伯即日起暫停所有國際客運航班，同時暫停人員經陸路及海上口岸入境。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2371585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2371585&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzEYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=f427fd3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2371585</a>"},{"pid":"1b0c059effd4375ebdc8d7d391a01af8aed0cead","tid":2334410,"uid":79174,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:10:51.000Z","msg":"印度神童又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0720000f465ce259b7e813df6dcd9262ddabe8","tid":2334410,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"幾時改名叫英國肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723278ea89066242188e5edd1068219a60bed851","tid":2334410,"uid":221530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e0720000f465ce259b7e813df6dcd9262ddabe8","tid":2334410,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"幾時改名叫英國肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"英國變種冠狀病毒肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3031b293e4f8e40c5cb332b25e40245da13247b1","tid":